title: [Vornavian Coast, Coastal Woods]
description: Bright moonlight flows in from the west, where the sounds of the crashing surf can be heard over the rushing winds and rustling leaves.  The woods here are lush, and thick underbrush covers the ground around the trees.  The cliff to the west can be climbed down to the beach.
